	<h1 class=hero>Our Design Process</h1>
	<p class=hero-sub-3>We believe that addressing healthcare is a multi-stage problem solving process that needs to put the <i>user</i> at the center of our thinking. Before we can make an impact, we need to understand.</p>
	
