	</ul>
	
	<div class="tab-content extra-space">
	  <div class="tab-pane fade in active" id="phase-1">
		<div class=row>
		<div class="col-xs-4 design-process">
		<h3 class=hero><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></span>Interview</h3>
		<p>We gain an understanding of our users through in-depth interviews with all stakeholders, including patients, physicians, health educators, care coordinators etc.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-xs-4 design-process">
		<h3 class=hero><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open"></span>Observe</h3>
		<p>We observe, document and evaluate patient visits, group meetings, diabetes classes, one-on-one health education appointments etc.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-xs-4 design-process">
		<h3 class=hero><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-circle"></span>Validate</h3>
		<p>We complement our findings with clinically-proven interventions and techniques, such as motivational interviewing and values based affirmation.</p>
		</div>
		
		</div><!--.row -->	
		
	  </div>
	  <div class="tab-pane fade" id="phase-2">
		
		<div class=row>
		<div class="col-xs-4 design-process">
		<h3 class=hero><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-edit"></span>Create</h3>
		<p>We take the immense quantity of data generated in Phase I to outline specific programs. These are structured as either short 4-6 week modules, or longer 3-12 month programs.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-xs-4 design-process">
		<h3 class=hero><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-stats"></span>Analyze</h3>
		<p>We also decide which metrics and overall trends — such as blood glucose, weight, medication adherence — are important to track for each program.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-xs-4 design-process">
		<h3 class=hero><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-saved"></span>Review</h3>
